        <item>
            <title>【现场评测】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 现埸实试　新焦段+轻巧+画质媲美第一代 G Master</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:30:12 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相机测试]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony G]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220886</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Sony 推出新 G 系列镜头 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G，属于全新焦段，同时继续轻巧的设计，放上 A7CII 的机身上感觉平衡。小编就参与了 Sony 的「试镜」活动，以下同大家分享在会场的试用感受，事不宜迟，马上实测！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220896 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06533-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06533-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06533-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220899 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07683-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07683-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07683-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Sony 推出新 G 系列镜头 Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G，</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>新镜新焦段，长度轻巧适中</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 属 Sony 镜头群的全新焦段，新镜造得更轻，只重 440 克，兼且有 F2.8 大光圈，更加有利低光时表现。新镜镜筒长 92.3mm，拎出街摄影或者放入相机袋，整体体积适中。配合 FX3、A7C 等细机时，机身与镜头的平衡也不俗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220897 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07673-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07673-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07673-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220908 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07679-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07679-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07679-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲整体体积适中，机身与镜头的平衡也不俗</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>MTF 曲线，画质媲美第一代 G Master</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 用上了 4 片非球面镜及 2 片的 ED 超低色散镜片有效地减少像差，亦以最佳方式抑制色差。FE 24-50mm F2.8 G，Sony 就提供了纯净的散景波波。波波里面的洋葱圈效果降得更加更加低。新镜最近对焦距离达 1:3，24mm 时有 0.19mm，50mm 时有 0.30mm。最大放大倍率 0.3 倍。 MTF 曲线显示，FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 画质可媲美第一代 G Master，在记者会中我们未能详细测试这方面，日后有机会再为镜头作深入评测。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220904 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06506-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06506-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06506-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220905 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06513-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06513-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06513-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220903 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3209-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3209-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3209.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MTF 曲线显示，FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 画质可媲美第一代 G Master</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/14/sony-ps5-slim-digital/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5 Slim + 光碟机开箱，安装示范 + 香港价钱 + 发售日期</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/10/test-sony-16-35mm-f2-8-gm-ii-lens/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony FE 16-35mm F2.8 GM II 广角变焦镜头，边缘成像超清 + 对焦准绳度高</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/sony-and-honda-ev-venture-to-launch-suv-and-compact-before-2030/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Sony、Honda 合资电动车品牌   Afeela 将添加 SUV 和小型车款</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>两线性摩打驱动，支援 120fps 高速连拍</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 内部对焦系统由两个线性摩打驱动，可宁静迅速地自动对焦。在寂静地方拍摄影片，都不用担心将摩打噪音收录到影片中。新镜能够配合最新的 A9III 拍摄 120fps 相片，亦支援 Dynamic Active 动态主动或 Avtive Mode 主动模式影像稳定功能，及相容于相机的对焦呼吸补偿功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220906 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06526-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06526-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06526-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220909 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07685-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07685-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07685-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220916 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07676-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07676-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07676-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 内部对焦系统由两个线性摩打驱动，可宁静迅速地自动对焦</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>操控具拍片特性</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 顾及了拍片的使用者，包括有光圈环及光圈点击开关，可选择 1/3 级，AF/MF 切换按钮及直接控制光圈。无段光圈环最重要是拍摄影片时，可顺滑地调整影片的景深，配合变焦焦点改变，可制造出极具创意的影像效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220907 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06537-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06537-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06537-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220910 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07687-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07687-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07687-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220911 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07686-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07686-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07686-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 顾及了拍片的使用者，有光圈环及光圈点击开关切换按钮及直接控制光圈，及 AF/MF 切换按钮及直接控制光圈</p><h2></h2><h2>香港价格、供应</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">FE 24-50mm F2.8 G</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">建议零售价：HK$8,990</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">预售日期：2024 年 2 月 27 日至 4 月 24 日</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">预计取货日期：2024 年 4 月 26 日起</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">预售地点：Sony Online Store，Sony 专门店，特约零售商</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">预售优惠：送多层镀膜保护滤镜 VF-67MPAM/2 SYH（价值 HK$530）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220917 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07679-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07679-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07679-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220918 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07682-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07682-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc07682-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220920 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06535-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06535-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06535-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220922 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06522-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06522-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06522-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220923 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06524-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06524-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06524-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220924 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06520-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06520-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc06520-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/14/sony-ps5-slim-digital/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5 Slim + 光碟机开箱，安装示范 + 香港价钱 + 发售日期</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/10/test-sony-16-35mm-f2-8-gm-ii-lens/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Sony FE 16-35mm F2.8 GM II 广角变焦镜头，边缘成像超清 + 对焦准绳度高</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/sony-and-honda-ev-venture-to-launch-suv-and-compact-before-2030/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Sony、Honda 合资电动车品牌   Afeela 将添加 SUV 和小型车款</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sony-fe-24-50mm-f2-8-g/dc/">【现场评测】Sony FE 24-50mm F2.8 G 现埸实试　新焦段+轻巧+画质媲美第一代 G Master</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
