        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【评测】Sennheiser ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 真无线蓝牙头戴式耳机　续航力够+音色甜美+性价比高</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sennheiser-accentum-plus-wireless/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sennheiser-accentum-plus-wireless</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sennheiser-accentum-plus-wireless/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:00:12 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sennheiser]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sennheiser ACCENTUM Plus Wireless]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220149</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Sennheiser 上年推出的 ACCENTUM Wireless 性价比高，成为入门级热门之选。事隔几个月后再推出新款无线蓝牙头戴式耳机 ACCENTUM Plus Wireless。新机承传了 Sennheiser 舒服的音色，价钱方面属中价位，但表现似乎不差过旗舰耳机，整体性价比都几高。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220340 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08863-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08863-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08863-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Sennheiser ACCENTUM Plus Wireless</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>黑白两色 </strong><strong>继续</strong><strong>低调设计不易留痕</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 的设计及外观颇为简洁，与 ACCENTUM Wireless 几乎一样，耳机只有侧面印有细小反光的 Sennheiser 标示，低调设计带点特色，同时不乏个性。机身用上了磨砂质地，摸上手舒适，不易留下指纹等污渍。ACCENTUM Wireless 都有 2 款颜色选择，小编拿到的是黑色，型格之选。另外还有白色，感觉比较优雅高贵，更会适合女士。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220339 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08831-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08831-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08831-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 的设计及外观颇为简洁</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220341 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08836-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08836-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08836-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲侧面印有细小反光的 Sennheiser 标示，低调设计带点特色</p><h2><strong>耳罩</strong><strong>不重</strong> <strong>佩戴感舒适</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 包装附送了 1 个收纳袋，里面有 1 条 USB-C 充电线、1 条 3.5 线及 1 份说明书。ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 是头罩式耳机，机身只重 22.7 克，小编戴了 3 小时感觉实净，耳罩用料记忆绵，亦不会轻易掉下，惟耳罩比较细小，空间感略嫌局促。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220342 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08837-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08837-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08837-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 包装附送了 1 个收纳袋</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220343 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08835-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08835-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08835-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳罩用料记忆绵，亦不会轻易掉下，惟耳罩比较细小，空间感略嫌局促</p><h2><strong>去除</strong><strong>实体键 </strong><strong>呈现高级感</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 去除了大部份实体键，只剩下了开机配对按键。今次采用了旗舰耳机的轻触式设计，感觉更加高级，却没有实体键的直接感，小编在调整耳机时，确实多次误触，导致出现错误指令，似乎是轻触式设计无法避免的意外。操控方面颇为简单，最底在 USB-C 充电口旁的按键是开关掣，长按 3 秒可开关，5 秒可连接蓝牙，连接速度快。控制音乐全在右边耳罩，按 1 下可暂停或继续播放音乐，按 2 下则可切换通透及主动降噪模式。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220344 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08833-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08833-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08833-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 去除了大部份实体键，只剩下了开机配对按键</p><h2><strong>Sennheiser Smart Control</strong> <strong>自定义</strong> <strong>EQ</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Sennheiser 向来都有自家应用程式，用家可以下载 Smart Control，调整主动降噪、通透模式、EQ 等。主动降噪可选择开启或关闭减少风声。EQ 方面就预设 2 项，分别是 Bass Boost 及 Podcast，假如用家对 EQ 未有太多认识，或许未能满足需求。Sennheiser 似乎鼓励用家自行调节。用家亦可自定通话时，聆听多少自己的声音。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220345 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3145-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3145-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3145.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220347 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3147-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3147-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3147.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220346 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3146-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3146-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3146.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家可以下载 Smart Control，调整主动降噪、通透模式、EQ 等</p><h2><strong>多装置连接，非常方便实用</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Sennheiser ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 有多装置连接，用家可同时连上电脑及手机，小编工作时经常不止用一个装置，所以觉得这功能非常实用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220348 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3144-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3144-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3144.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Sennheiser ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 有多装置连接，方便实用</p><h2><strong>支援快速充电，充电</strong> <strong>10 分钟可用 5 小时</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">续航力方面，充满电的 ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 可以连续使用 50 小时，超长的使用时间足够小编用 4 至 5 日。ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 支援快速充电，只要充电 10 分钟，即可使用 5 小时，可谓是惊人，而总充电时间需要 3.5 小时。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220350 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08869-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08869-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08869-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 支援快速充电，只要充电 10 分钟，即可使用 5 小时，可谓是惊人</p><h2>比上代 ACCENTUM Wireless 多了 1 个收音咪</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">由于可在 Sennheiser Smart Control 内调整聆听多少自己的声音，加上有 Hybrid ANC，因此 ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 通话表现良好，如果在室内通话绝对没问题，室外可能会有少许风噪声。今代比上代 ACCENTUM Wireless 多了 1 个收音咪，有助提升主动降噪功能。由于支援最普遍的 SBC、AAC、aptX 及 aptX Adptive 的基本规格，能更高清传送予用家，而音质表现非常不错，亦因此确保音乐来源的质素。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220349 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08860-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08860-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc08860-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 通话表现良好</p><h2><strong>人声低频柔和</strong> <strong>三频平衡好</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">小编在 iPhone 上使用 Moov 播放吴雨霏的《生命树》，人声靠前，音色甜美。再试听谢霆锋的《游乐场》，人声仍然出位，音乐分析力好，加上小许且不杂乱的电结他声，高频不俗，低音结他柔和，力度足够。再听听编曲比较复杂黄贯中的《天与地》，不感到音乐太杂乱，人声依旧相对靠前，调节 EQ 后使低频更突出。小编认为 ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 比较适合听流行歌，音色甜美。</p><h2><strong><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220351 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3141-313x580.jpg" alt="" width="313" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3141-313x580.jpg 313w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3141.jpg 485w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 313px" /></strong></h2><p style="text-align: center;">▲吴雨霏《生命树》，人声靠前，音色甜美</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220352 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3143-315x580.jpg" alt="" width="315" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3143-315x580.jpg 315w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3143.jpg 488w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 315px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲谢霆锋《游乐场》，人声仍然出位，音乐分析力好</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1220353 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3142-313x580.jpg" alt="" width="313" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3142-313x580.jpg 313w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3142.jpg 485w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 313px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲编曲比较复杂黄贯中的《天与地》，不感到音乐太杂乱，人声依旧相对靠前</p><h2><strong>总结：音色</strong><strong>甜美</strong> <strong>续航力够</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 的售价为 HK$ 1999，属中价位，但做到高水准，的确有 Sennheiser 的高级感和音色，再加上续航力达 50 小时。如此的规格，性价比极高，适合有要求的使用者。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/sennheiser-accentum-plus-wireless/mobile-music/headphones/">【评测】Sennheiser ACCENTUM Plus Wireless 真无线蓝牙头戴式耳机　续航力够+音色甜美+性价比高</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
